<subSubSection box="[199,1315,1913,1938]" pageId="8" pageNumber="212" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1409,1938]" box="[199,1315,1913,1938]" pageId="8" pageNumber="212">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1913,1937]" pageId="8" pageNumber="212">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name refers to the colouration of the forewing; Latin: rufa—red, brunnea—brown.
